Describtion:
````````````
This script generates a map grid in osm xml.

Parameter
 - left,right,top,bottom				(map area)
 - xpos,ypos										(start position/top left corner of the grid)
 - delta_X,delta_y							(x/y difference between two lines in degree)
 - boarder_high/boarder_width		(size of the grid boarder)


Usage:
``````
Use my script with get request (URL-Comming soon)
Or download the PHP-File and run it localy.
After you have done this you can load it as source in Maperitive and apply
a special renderrule to visualize the grid. (See Examples)


Examples:
`````````
